Package: jbig2pdf
Architecture: all
Depends:
 ${misc:Depends},
 ${python:Depends},
 ${shlibs:Depends}
Recommends: jbig2enc
Description: Python script to convert jbig2 files to PDF files
 This package contains a script called pdf.py (FIXME: bad name) that is
 meant to "join" all the JBIG2 files generated by jbig2(enc) in a single PDF
 file.
 .
 If multiple files are converted at the same time, their commonalities
 (e.g., the shapes of letters) are stored in a symbol dictionary that this
 script can use to make the PDF files competitive even with alternative
 formats meant for scanned documents (e.g., DjVu files).
